F":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c653%2c20220316%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,653,20220316,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"653","JDATE":"20220316","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}